  "id": "RAW_ecae7dd4",
  "title": "冲上苹果付费榜一的死了么，让我重新思考和 AI 相处的意义",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3MTk3NzYzNw==&mid=2247503977&idx=1&sn=eeb76776bc52fe327baa68414bc71fe1",
  "date": "2026-01-12 01:45:00",
  "author": "卡尔的AI沃茨",
  "siteName": "卡尔的AI沃茨",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span style=\"white-space-collapse:preserve;letter-spacing:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">这两天我们一起见证了一个带点荒诞现实的时刻，</span></p>\n  <div data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"border:1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);border-radius:12px;padding:0px 0px;margin:0px 0px;font-weight:400;font-family:PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"border:1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);border-radius:12px;padding:0px 0px;margin:0 0px;color:#8f959e;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-family:PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"border:1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);border-radius:12px;padding:0px 0px;margin:0 0px;color:#8f959e;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-family:PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个叫死了么（不是饿了么）的 App 冲上了苹果付费榜第一。我也花八块钱买了，没有复杂功能，UI朴素到像个假软件。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">填上名字，填紧急联系人邮箱，然后每天点一下签到。如果连续两天没签到，死了么就会发邮件给紧急联系人。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">这就是它现在所有的功能了。&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\n     <div style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;display: block;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: center !important;\">\n      <p style=\"display: block;margin: 0px;border-radius: 0px;line-height: 2em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100020317\" data-ratio=\"0.9796296296296296\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 5px;box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;border: 0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);padding: 0px;box-shadow: none;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0eafc16a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXkVqsmRrSRqCFSicM5TRSgDiaiavSfJebhQzvXDBkcZqUibDHfPAnicvt8nSVr9WiaGsPe783guJnicsJ0icg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     </div>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">作为一个开发了四年的App，在某书上一搜一大把类似的开发思路，它火得超快，争议来得更快。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">有人觉得这是独居时代的救命绳，有人觉得名字晦气，有人担心隐私，有人吐槽两天就触发太容易误伤，有人又说可怕的并不是误报，而是根本没人会打开那封邮件。还有人翻出它从一块钱涨到八块钱了，就是靠着情绪割韭菜。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5333333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100020320\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6d8e4cd0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXkVqsmRrSRqCFSicM5TRSgDiaKu4OJKoXYK1tOdjpWLqtwqKZ0JxnKXyDjia5PW5IJkb0Ke6UibPSjh6w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我反而觉得，它能冲到付费榜第一，</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">核心原因不在功能，不在定价，</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">而在它把一个平时没什么人愿意说出口的恐惧，直接丢上台面，想要假装看不见都不行的那种。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">到2030年国内独居人口可能达到2亿，独居的人害怕可能不只是死亡，死亡至少还有仪式和确认。更折磨的是失联，手机没通知，消息发出去没回复，临时想找人吃个火锅发现整个城市里能叫出来的人没几个（我的经历）。</span></span></p>\n     <div style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;display: block;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: center !important;\">\n      <p style=\"display: block;margin: 0px;border-radius: 0px;line-height: 2em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 5px;box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;border: 0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);padding: 0px;box-shadow: none;\" data-imgfileid=\"100020315\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b6053323&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXkVqsmRrSRqCFSicM5TRSgDiaGL7y9ibAXjL4O4Lkm07fIzHONFcE0buwIbbRKibZkkWBKrVmajAOBlEQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     </div>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">死了么实际更像个失联确认器，</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">它把存在感做成了一个动作，把被看见做成了一个协议。你每天按一下，等于对世界说一声我还在。你不按，系统就代你对最关心你的人说一声TA可能不在了。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">让我觉得有点割裂的点是它太简单了，简单到我第一次用就能像个产品经理一样提十几条意见，</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们拥有信息度最密集的通信App，社交软件一层套一层，每天几千条消息提醒。按道理说没时间也没心情感到孤独吧，但就是会在某一个晚上甚至某一个瞬间，大脑会停下所有的运转来思考我活在这个世界上的意义。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以，</span></span><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们</span></span><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">可能就是在这个阶段就是</span></span><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">需要</span></span><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">这样</span></span><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个极端简陋的打卡按钮，来证明自己仍然活在关系里。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">这种矛盾归类为现代性孤独，</span></span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">外部连接越多，内在关系越稀薄。</span></span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">雪莉·特克尔写过类似的观察，技术让我们可以随时在线，也让我们更容易一个人待着，更擅长回避真实的麻烦。这个时代的孤独不是没人说话，是不敢打扰真实环境里的别人，正常沟通都成了一种打扰</span></span></p>\n     <div style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;display: block;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: center !important;\">\n      <p style=\"display: block;margin: 0px;border-radius: 0px;line-height: 2em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3962962962962964\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 5px;box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;border: 0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);padding: 0px;box-shadow: none;\" data-imgfileid=\"100020316\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=577d13a7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXkVqsmRrSRqCFSicM5TRSgDiaRKbJW5V213xwzNbWtFiau6YibpXKVuCjiaHJb1mUG5j9icX1dR0kkLFE1A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     </div>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">死了么的评论区里还有一大半的评论是在讨论替代方案的，能不能被动打卡，通过蓝牙设备连接数量，手机打开频率，能不能用短信，用微信推送，能不能识别手机定位，看看有没有出门走路。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我也想vibe coding一把，再现一个传奇的2小时零基础小白从零到App上线的AI奇迹。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以“活着没”上线了，不需要担心隐私，是调用本地邮箱来发送邮件的，让大家可以免费过过手瘾。</span></span></p>\n     <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">🔗 ai.studio/apps/drive/1ekJCnJ1l8uU2hlomuzV4lMvuBQNFRv4Z</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我想过细化后，至少把短信通